{"word":"G4332 - προσεδρεύω - prosedreúō - pros-ed-ryoo'-o - Wait at","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσεδρεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prosedreúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pros-ed-ryoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Wait at</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பணிவிடை"},{"paragraph":"1. properly, to sit near"},{"paragraph":"2. to attend assiduously"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G4314 - πρός - prós - pros/4314\">G4314</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G1476 - ἑδραῖος - hedraîos - hed-rah'-yos/1476\">G1476</a>; to <i>sit near</i>, that is, <i>attend</i> as a servant: - wait at.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}